mat_beg mat_light emission 8.0 255,255,255 mat_end
f 9 8 10 mat_light
f 10 11 9 mat_light
f 9 8 12 mat_light
f 12 13 9 mat_light
f 8 10 14 mat_light
f 14 12 8 mat_light
f 11 10 14 mat_light
f 14 15 11 mat_light
f 9 11 15 mat_light
f 15 13 9 mat_light
